## Credential Rule

Never write credentials, API keys, or tokens into any file in this vault. It syncs to Obsidian. Secrets live in `C:\Users\brent\.maaxgen\` only.

## Safety Rules

Do not make live changes to ad accounts, websites, automations, emails, or SMS campaigns without explicit human approval.

Read-only analysis is allowed.

Draft recommendations are allowed.

Publishing or editing live assets requires approval.
